OL,3,C#800 fine dished out to Croydon man
OL,4,Cfor littering cigarette butt
OL,6,FA man from Croydon has been fined more
OL,7,Fthan #800 for throwing a cigarette
OL,8,Fbutt on the floor in Market Square,
OL,9,FBromley.
OL,11,FCarl Smith, 31, was issued with a #100
OL,12,Ffixed penalty notice earlier this year
OL,13,Ffor dropping the butt on the street,
OL,14,FBromley Council said.
OL,16,FHe was then prosecuted after he failed
OL,17,Fto pay the notice for littering,
OL,18,Fcontrary to the Environmental
OL,19,FProtection Act.
