OL,3,C#800 fine dished out to Croydon man
OL,4,Cfor littering cigarette butt
OL,6,FSmith pleaded guilty by the single
OL,7,Fjustice procedure on December 3. He
OL,8,Fwas subsequently ordered to pay #833
OL,9,Fby Bromley Magistrates' Court. The
OL,10,Famount included a fine of #293, a
OL,11,Fsurcharge of #117 and costs of #423 to
OL,12,Fbe paid by January 14.
OL,14,FBromley Council said it was the 12th
OL,15,Fprosecution it had carried out for
OL,16,Flittering since the beginning of
OL,17,FSeptember.
