OL,6,FIt added that they serve as a "warning
OL,7,Fto others to not discard unwanted
OL,8,Fitems in the street, but to place them
OL,9,Fin a litter bin or take rubbish home".
OL,11,FA Bromley Council spokesperson said:
OL,12,F"On behalf of residents, the council
OL,13,Fhas street-cleaning teams working
OL,14,Fseven days a week across the borough,
OL,15,Fkeeping our streets neat.
OL,17,F"Littering undoes this work and is
OL,18,Fillegal, with our enforcement team
OL,19,Fissuing a fixed penalty notice to
OL,20,Fanyone seen littering.
